rows.label: xs33570100_MSG0010
rows.name:
Let this be a lesson, never leave home without
a full bottle of hooch...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs33570100_MSG0020
rows.name:

some liquid courage right about now...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs33570100_MSG0030
rows.name:

Nah, I'm not really surprised.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs33570100_MSG0040
rows.name:
We took a bit of a bruising,
but it'll take more than that to keep you down, right?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs33570100_MSG0050
rows.name:
Will I help? Oh, sure thing!
It's in the job description, after all.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs33570100_MSG0060
rows.name:
